507
00:36:03.786 --> 00:36:05.163
I hope she can take it.

508
00:36:07.456 --> 00:36:09.208
Hello. sir. This way.

509
00:36:24.015 --> 00:36:26.225
Stop. Now show us the stairs.

510
00:36:26.309 --> 00:36:27.935
