511
00:36:28.561 --> 00:36:29.395
Why not?

512
00:36:29.478 --> 00:36:30.813
We just don't.

513
00:36:33.149 --> 00:36:34.859
Are you kidding me? You shit...

514
00:36:35.818 --> 00:36:37.778
So. tell me something.

515
00:36:38.446 --> 00:36:40.823
